04-11T02:05:46.000+00:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be/-/commit/2b2891db4e52214f97631b91cbe1f50256322411\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"ea3f287a29bd18dbd9ee96de14d6bf27f5be238f\",\n    \"short_id\": \"ea3f287a\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-11T01:51:31.000+00:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"c480be9cd6eca99b315296f59d871f21a759348a\"\n    ],\n    \"title\": \"perf: enhancement ui ux, time reload, animation for this website\",\n    \"message\": \"perf: enhancement ui ux, time reload, animation for this website\\n\",\n    \"author_name\": \"Cipher (Agent 03)\",\n    \"author_email\": \"cipher@openclaw.dev\",\n    \"authored_date\": \"2026-04-11T01:51:31.000+00:00\",\n    \"committer_name\": \"Cipher (Agent 03)\",\n    \"committer_email\": \"cipher@openclaw.dev\",\n    \"committed_date\": \"2026-04-11T01:51:31.000+00:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be/-/commit/ea3f287a29bd18dbd9ee96de14d6bf27f5be238f\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"c480be9cd6eca99b315296f59d871f21a759348a\",\n    \"short_id\": \"c480be9c\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-11T01:28:06.000+00:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"0a905965f75613b557cd3ded036fa18ef9d52c8c\",\n      \"bc2834b73d1b78e68bdab9334f153aca268ea94c\"\n    ],\n    \"title\": \"merge: fix conflict merge request from develop\",\n    \"message\": \"merge: fix conflict merge request from develop\\n\",\n    \"author_name\": \"Cipher (Agent 03)\",\n    \"author_email\": \"cipher@openclaw.dev\",\n    \"authored_date\": \"2026-04-11T01:28:06.000+00:00\",\n    \"committer_name\": \"Cipher (Agent 03)\",\n    \"committer_email\": \"cipher@openclaw.dev\",\n    \"committed_date\": \"2026-04-11T01:28:06.000+00:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be/-/commit/c480be9cd6eca99b315296f59d871f21a759348a\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"id\": \"0a905965f75613b557cd3ded036fa18ef9d52c8c\",\n    \"short_id\": \"0a905965\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-04-10T10:34:12.000+00:00\",\n    \"parent_ids\": [\n      \"70abf1b819b45542e865b2a49095bf7a1567ffc6\"\n    ],\n    \"title\": \"fix: lift progress_flags to root via $addFields before $project\",\n    \"message\": \"fix: lift progress_flags to root via $addFields before $project\\n\\nCannot mix inclusion/exclusion in same $project stage (MongoDB restriction).\\nSolution: use $addFields before $project to promote\\nlatest_enrollment.progress_flags to root level, keeping $project\\nas a pure exclusion projection (all exclusions, no inclusions).\\n\",\n    \"author_name\": \"Cipher (Agent 03)\",\n    \"author_email\": \"cipher@openclaw.dev\",\n    \"authored_date\": \"2026-04-10T10:29:29.000+00:00\",\n    \"committer_name\": \"Cipher (Agent 03)\",\n    \"committer_email\": \"cipher@openclaw.dev\",\n    \"committed_date\": \"2026-04-10T10:34:12.000+00:00\",\n    \"trailers\": {},\n    \"extended_trailers\": {},\n    \"web_url\": \"https://gitlab.com/ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be/-/commit/0a905965f75613b557cd3ded036fa18ef9d52c8c\"\n  }\n]"}],"details":{"mcpServer":"gitlab","mcpTool":"gitlab_list_commits"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776058767539}}
{"type":"message","id":"c5b0faf7","parentId":"919dc510","timestamp":"2026-04-13T05:39:45.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me compile the QLHV dev workflow report for Lead.\n\nKey findings:\n1. **Dev là người thật** — `khuong ninh` (Ninh Thanh Khuong) — người dev đang làm việc trực tiếp trên GitLab\n2. **Dev push thẳng lên develop** — không qua branch → MR workflow\n3. Các agents (Cipher Agent 03) cũng push lên develop trực tiếp\n4. Hiện có 3 MR đang mở: #6 (conflict), #7 (can_be_merged), #8 (unchecked)\n\n\n5. Tôi đang kiểm tra các yêu cầu về git workflow — dev đang push trực tiếp lên develop thay vì tạo feature branches, và mặc dù có MR #7 và #8, chúng không tuân theo quy trình branch → MR → review đầy đủ.","thinkingSignature":"ff2cdd3cc75be437378d5ec85a4bbbd2e651d8b3bfcf186cc9480b32b726227c"},{"type":"text","text":"**Báo cáo Workflow QLHV — Phát hiện vấn đề nghiêm trọng:**\n\n---\n\n## 👤 Ai đang làm việc?\n\n| | |\n|---|---|\n| **Human Dev** | Ninh Thanh Khuong (`khuong ninh`) — push trực tiếp lên develop |\n| **OpenClaw Agent** | Cipher Agent 03 — push lên develop |\n\n---\n\n## 🔴 Vấn đề: Dev push THẲNG LÊN develop\n\n```\nkhuong ninh: eb167e93 — feat: update student, exam, lesson...\nkhuong ninh: 2b2891db — Merge feat/database-master → develop  (direct merge)\nCipher Agent 03: ea3f287a — perf: enhancement ui ux...       (direct commit)\nCipher Agent 03: c480be9c — merge: fix conflict MR from develop (direct)\n```\n\n**Dev push thẳng lên develop như thường — không tạo branch, không MR.**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 MRs hiện tại (BE):\n\n| MR | Branch | Status | Author |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **#6** | `feat/notification-migration` | 🔴 **conflict** | khuong ninh |\n| **#7** | `fix/auth-registration-bug` | ✅ **mergeable** | khuong ninh |\n| **#8** | `feat/student-import-background` | ⏳ unchecked | khuong ninh |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Không tuân thủ Git Workflow mới\n\n**Thực tế:**\n- ❌ Không tạo branch cho mỗi task\n- ❌ Không chạy lint/build/test trước push\n- ❌ MR #6 để bị conflict 2 ngày không xử lý\n- ❌ Dev push trực tiếp lên develop\n\n**Yêu cầu mới của Lead:**\n- ✅ Mỗi task = branch mới từ `develop`\n- ✅ lint → build → test → push → MR → Lead review\n- ❌ KHÔNG push thẳng lên develop\n\n---\n\nLead muốn Orbis **enforce quy trình này** xuống dev (khuong ninh) không? Hay chỉ enforce cho các agent OpenClaw thôi?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1798,"output":777,"cacheRead":34928,"cacheWrite":4166,"totalTokens":41669,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776058767659,"responseId":"062bb490e01b7dd4fa2f4745da6777cc"}}
