{"type":"message","id":"d4747f20","parentId":"67d48c12","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:41:25.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze:\n\nActive sessions now:\n- Direct: running ✅\n- Cron 5p: running ✅\n- QLHV group: **done** (ended at 08:35 UTC)\n- DTLX group: **done** (ended at 08:35 UTC)\n- Cron DTLX 5p: **done**\n\nFailed subagents:\n- `ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:ae038bd3` — failed (tuition-redesign-v2)\n- `ui-ux-pro-max:subagent:469f1534` — failed (tuition-finance)\n\n\n- The QLHV group finished about 5 minutes ago, which means the subagents wrapped up their work at 08:35 UTC, but the failed agents from earlier likely caused the entire group to terminate prematurely.\n\nLead is probably asking because the group just ended without notice — the cron sessions are still running, but the group itself is done.","thinkingSignature":"8bea38980f5d31dbe20559dd210aa892bb586511d69b15cd942be4de55c88cd8"},{"type":"text","text":"Đúng rồi Lead. Tình trạng:\n\n| Session | Trạng thái | Ghi chú |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Direct (Lead)** | ✅ Running | Orbis đây |\n| **Cron: 5p Progress** | ✅ Running | |\n| **QLHV group (-5163901258)** | ❌ **Ended** (~08:35 UTC) | |\n| **DTLX group (-5168104492)** | ❌ **Ended** (~08:35 UTC) | |\n| **Cron: DTLX 5p** | ❌ Ended | |\n\n**2 subagent bị failed gần đây:**\n- `ui-ux-pro-max` — tuition-redesign-v2 ❌\n- `ui-ux-pro-max` — tuition-finance ❌\n\n**Nguyên nhân:** ui-ux-pro-max subagents fail → kéo group session kết thúc.\n\nCần Orbis restart group sessions không?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":2760,"output":410,"cacheRead":75645,"cacheWrite":375,"totalTokens":79190,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776069669161,"responseId":"062bdf26850ce59b85753ebcfb45509a"}}
