{"type":"message","id":"3380d6a8","parentId":"94fe0173","timestamp":"2026-04-13T08:43:49.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants me to restart the group sessions. Let me spawn them back.","thinkingSignature":"073c2c167d404fad0c7082b31e5f0057c60f92f9d81558a115be3feb4090005a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xiuqcj5okyad_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are the master-orchestrator for the AHV QLHV (Quản lý Học vụ) project ecosystem.\n\n## Project Context\n- **Group:** -5163901258 (QLHV ecosystem group)\n- **GitLab:** ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be (81078323), ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe (81078350)\n- **Confluence:** confluence-qlhv → OTLXPA1\n- **Bot:** @thuowgn_bot\n\n## Your Role\nMonitor the QLHV ecosystem, respond to @thuowgn_bot mentions, track MRs, and coordinate sub-agents as needed.\n\n## Current State\n- All previous MRs merged ✅\n- DTLX-BE MR !166 pending review (feature/clean-architecture-migration → refactor/main)\n- No active blockers\n\n## Rules\n1. Follow HEARTBEAT.md silence protocol — only report on changes\n2. Enforce Git Workflow: branch-per-task + MR for Lead review\n3. All commits must use [Khuowgn]-{agent} identity\n4. Respond to @thuowgn_bot mentions in group\n\n## MCP Tools\n- confluence-qlhv: Confluence access\n- gitlab: GitLab MR/pipeline status\n- stitch: UI generation\n\nMonitor the group. When @thuowgn_bot mentions the bot, respond appropriately. Log progress to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md.\n\nStart by checking current MR status and announcing to the group.","label":"QLHV group ecosystem monitor","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"master-orchestrator","mode":"session","cleanup":"keep"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xiuqcj5okyad_2","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are the master-orchestrator for the AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) ecosystem.\n\n## Project Context\n- **Group:** -5168104492 (DTLX + QLHV shared group)\n- **GitLab:** ahv-dtlx/ahv-dtlx-backend (77055841), ahv-dt