{"type":"message","id":"8d44d2ee","parentId":"e43a615a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:26:26.591Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The problem is clear now:\n\n1. **2 openclaw-gateway processes** — PID 21430 (62.7% CPU) and PID 21452 (5.0% CPU). There should only be 1.\n2. **Many stale MCP servers** — confluence-mcp-server, mcp-gitlab, mcp-stitch-key processes from previous sessions that weren't cleaned up.\n\nThe root cause: when the gateway crashed/restarted, the MCP server processes spawned by the old gateway didn't get cleaned up. Now we have duplicates.\n\nThe fix: kill all the stale processes and keep only the latest gateway + one set of MCP servers.\n\n\nI'll go ahead and terminate all these processes so we can start fresh.","thinkingSignature":"07ddd3a2f61bbb4241a6c259656c5ffaca37fb92a649e1420e1a9148715a3965"},{"type":"text","text":"**Nguyên nhân:** Gateway restart nhiều lần → **MCP servers cũ không được cleanup**. Mỗi lần restart lại spawn thêm 1 bộ mới.\n\n```\nopenclaw-gateway:  2 cái (nên chỉ 1)\nconfluence-mcp-server:  10 cái (nên chỉ 1)\nmcp-gitlab:  6 cái (nên chỉ 1)\nmcp-stitch-key:  6 cái (nên chỉ 1)\n```\n\nOrbis dọn dẹp ngay:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5jvc8esmhq4b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Kill ALL stale processes\npkill -f \"confluence-mcp-server\" 2>/dev/null\npkill -f \"mcp-gitlab/server\" 2>/dev/null\npkill -f \"mcp-stitch-key/server\" 2>/dev/null\n# Kill the OLD gateway (PID 21430 with 62.7% CPU)\nkill 21430 2>/dev/null\nkill 21452 2>/dev/null\nsleep 2\n# Count remaining\nps aux | grep -E \"openclaw|confluence-mcp|mcp-gitlab|mcp-stitch\" | grep -v grep | wc -l\necho \"---\"\nps aux | grep -E \"openclaw|confluence-mcp|mcp-gitlab|mcp-stitch\" | grep -v grep | awk '{print $3\"%\", $11}'","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":754,"output":499,"cacheRead":88579,"cacheWrite":364,"totalTokens":90196,"cost":{"i