{"type":"message","id":"c48e67c1","parentId":"b444a8b3","timestamp":"2026-04-14T02:44:42.708Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Nhầm rồi. DTLX group (-5168104492) giữ nguyên — cần hoạt động vì đang test API.\n\nOrbis vừa check: group session đã **ended** lúc ~02:31 UTC. Cần restart lại."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"sessions_send-1776134675776445056-71411","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492","message":"Resume: Lead yêu cầu tiếp tục task test API module auth trên ahv-dtlx-backend. \n\nTình trạng lần cuối:\n- DTLX FE: ✅ port 3000 running\n- DTLX BE: ❌ Build fail — 35+ TypeScript errors (interface mismatch: data vs docs, limit vs itemsPerPage) trên branch feature/clean-architecture-migration\n- deploy-be subagent: timeout (SIGKILL sau 451s)\n\nCần:\n1. Fix TypeScript errors trong ahv-dtlx-backend\n2. Build thành công\n3. Start BE server\n4. Test API module auth\n\nTiếp tục đi. Không cần spawn subagent TroLy model. Dùng AHV-Holding-DEV.","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":153131,"output":384,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":153515,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776134645764,"responseId":"req_vrtx_011Ca2tudSu8GqRArK34cFL5"}}
